            <ab>P. L. Bat. 25 78 (English)

                                        (1st hand) - - - thirty-four gold solidi, total gld sol. 34, as well as eighty artabas of wheat (measured) with the measure of The-, together this totals 80 art. wheat and 34 gld. sil. in all.
                                        Makarios, stenographer and scribe, agrees.
                                        (2nd hand) (cross) Daniel agrees.
                                        (3rd hand) (cross) Makare agrees.</ab>
